The methodology for this project involves using ServiceNow Import Sets and Transform Maps to automate data import and relationship mapping.

Collect and prepare data from external sources (e.g., Excel file)
Upload data into Import Set (staging table)
Define Transform Map to map source fields to target table fields
Apply field mapping and data transformation rules
Use scripts to handle complex mappings (e.g., manager reference)
Execute transformation to load data into the target table
Use Dot Walking to access and manage related table data efficiently

This methodology ensures accurate, automated, and efficient data integration.
